                <h4 class="owner-title">MANAGEMENT/TEAM LEADER & EDUCATOR</h4>
                <h4 class="owner-title">Certified LICENSED BODYWORKER</h4>
                <p>Essa joined Meraki in June of 2018 just after she graduated her massage program at the Vancouver School of Healing Arts. She brings a yoga background to her knowledge which helps her understand the body and what it might need in a more informed manner.</p>
                <p>After dealing with her own shoulder injuries over the years she finds that this area of the body is one she understands deeply, and is always happy to help clients gain back their mobility. We are proud to say that Essa holds many titles at Meraki, she trains and develops all new staff, as well as managing the day-to-day operations. She’s always available to assist clients and staff with achieving their goals. Essa brings a nurturing touch to her treatments and loves to share a good laugh!</p>
